Merry Land and Investment Co Incsaid it will offer two million shares of common stock for sale.    Merry Land said it filed a registration statement with theSecurity and Exchange Commission. It also said the sale will beoffered through an underwriting group managed by &lt;Johnson,Lane, Space, Smith and Co Inc>, and Interstate Securities Corp&lt;IS>.    Proceeds will be used to reduce short-term debt, thecompany said. Reuter&#3;